OL,3,C'I was destroying my family':
OL,4,CSynthetic opioid addictions on the rise
OL,6,FA father-of-two says he almost lost
OL,7,Feverything because of an addiction to
OL,8,Fsynthetic opioids.
OL,10,FBob, whose name we've changed to
OL,11,Fprotect his identity, says his
OL,12,Faddiction began in 2019 when he was
OL,13,Fprescribed pain killers for a health
OL,14,Fcondition. He says he then
OL,15,F'manipulated' the health system by
OL,16,Fexaggerating his pain to get the
OL,17,Fstronger drugs.
