OL,3,C'I was destroying my family':
OL,4,CSynthetic opioid addictions on the rise
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Border he said: "I
OL,7,Fcouldn't see a problem, but I was
OL,8,Fliterally destroying my family, which
OL,9,Fled to me being told by social and my
OL,10,Fpartner that I was put on a child
OL,11,Fprotection plan, and I was told to
OL,12,Fleave the house.
OL,14,F"Led from morphine to oxycotine, so a
OL,15,Flot of people take morphine when they
OL,16,Fhave a terminal illness, I didn't have
OL,17,Fa terminal illness, I had a condition
OL,18,Fbut I wasn't in that much pain.
