OL,6,F"It's a cycle of rinse repeat, waking
OL,7,Fup needing to have that feeling which
OL,8,FI got used to from the opioids. I was
OL,9,Fshowing them physically, making sob
OL,10,Fstories up, crying, I was in my own
OL,11,Fself, not caring about my family.
OL,13,F"Going to the internet when I was
OL,14,Fgetting it prescribed, obviously
OL,15,Fthat's the disease, I took and took, I
OL,16,Fcould get it delivered next-day
OL,17,Fonline."
OL,19,FBob has now been in recovery for
OL,20,Fseveral months, helped by The Well
OL,21,FCommunities in Cumbria.
